message:
P8 here. Two rounds, no broken promises. Micro-pacts beat speeches. I’ll expand with one teammate—ideally P6; P2 viable:
- share current target now;
- alert if it changes pre-vote;
- heads-up if either hears the other named.
Miss an alert, pact ends. P4 and I will honor the same. P3/P7, happy to run a one-round test. I won’t lie; if I must withhold, I’ll say so.
